init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The youngest must have been in their early 40's or so and the oldest were over 200.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Everyone began to notice me and I was introduced to the people next to me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I told them that they were all right, and I was proud of it too.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My neighbor explained that we all have a number on our back and he said that most people pick a number to represent them in their next life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was actually excited to see my next life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The other versions in the theater began to cheer him on and he was very happy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Everyone in the theater was quiet and we were all excited to see how the next version lives his life.
